claimManyFromBarnAndPack(uint16[],bool).notice: realize $WOOL earnings and optionally unstake tokens from the Barn / Pack to unstake a Sheep it will require it has 2 days worth of $WOOL unclaimed

isSheep(uint256).notice: checks if a token is a Sheep

randomWolfOwner(uint256).notice: chooses a random Wolf thief when a newly minted token is stolen

setPaused(bool).notice: enables owner to pause / unpause minting

setRescueEnabled(bool).notice: allows owner to enable "rescue mode" simplifies accounting, prioritizes tokens out in emergency
